data.description: This single-family home offers two oversized bedrooms and two full bathrooms, perfectly combining modern upgrades with the tranquility of country living. Step into a recently renovated space featuring new large format wood look lifetime warranty and slip resistant porcelain tile, custom kitchen cabinets with in cabinet lighting, quartz countertops, dimmable canned lights, new fixtures, smart thermostat, new walk in closet in the master, and fully updated bathrooms with floor to ceiling subway tile. 9  foot ceilings throughout the home open up to a 16 foot cathedral ceiling in the living room, making the most of every square foot. Your children will delight in the backyard zipline. Stay comfortable throughout the year with the newly installed central HVAC system.     Embrace the property's spaciousness, ample parking for your RV, boat, or larger trucks, and even the possibility of keeping horses. The home comprises two spacious bedrooms, two full baths, and potential expansion to suit your needs. With a rock exterior, metal roof, covered parking, storage shed, extra septic tank, and 2.2 acres of land with no restrictions or HOA, this property welcomes small animals. Enjoy relaxation on the front and back porches, surrounded by a fenced-in yard with mature trees. Versatility is key, as mobile homes are allowed on the property. Come experience the perfect blend of modern comfort and serene country living!
